conditions:

conditional block(code) will be executed only if the certain condition is satisfied.

ex:
if
if else
if elif



conditions for int/float:
--------------------------
==
!=
>
<
>=
<=


condition for str:
-----------------------
==
!=



Block:
---------
if
else
for
while
class
funtion
try
except
finally

block contains sequence/group of code.
every block should start with ":"
and block code should be written with indentation.







